QuestData.Title: Hivethief's Jelly Stash
QuestData.Description:
This ettin was a well known and oft dreaded face among the bees of the Honeyback hive. Their jelly stores will benefit from his demise.
The Hivemother will be interested in this item.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Hivethief's Jelly Stash to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Take the Hivethief's Jelly Stash to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
